<br>
I missed Jibober what can I say? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I missed standing on hilltops casting bolts of fire down on my foes and then having them collide with the wall that is my &quot;pet&quot; (never liked that term...it sounds to docile...I prefer &quot;elemental servant!&quot;) and dash itself to pieces on it.  As well as sucking up my damage shields.  I missed having an utterly loyal minion who would cover my retreats when things went wrong.  I missed being able to summon up whatever I needed (and boy that's gotten MUCH better with the focus items etc!).  I missed camping infinite hours for Quillmane (oops!  How did THAT get in there?)<br>
<br>
Mages rule! <p><BR>
